                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>Now that the Blue Devils have developed into a top-10 defense, however, it becomes all the more important for Carter to maintain his defensive presence and continue to lead a unit that could help bring a sixth national title back to Durham.</p>
<p>“I’m just a player who wants to win,” Carter said. “I don’t care if I’m having two points, three points a game. As long as we’re winning, that’s what I care about.”</p>
